; Synthetic KAG .ks fixture (CC0, authored) — message text + #name state.
; Exercises: narration (no speaker), #name set, #voice/display split,
; a text line split into two runs by an inline [r] line-break tag, and a
; bare-# speaker reset. No choices, no jumps, no TJS — a clean text+name
; trace with zero diagnostics.
*start|Prologue
A quiet morning at the terminal.
#Alice
Good morning, world.
This line[r] continues after a tag.
#voice_042/Bob Sensei
Ah, Alice. You are early today.
#
Narration returns once the speaker is cleared.
